</sect1>

<sect1 id="newstuff-config">
<title>New Stuff</title>

<para>
The <guibutton>Download new vocabulary</guibutton> on the <guilabel>Vocabularies</guilabel> 
configuration page allows you to obtain new vocabulary files from the Internet:
</para>

<screenshot>
<screeninfo>&kanagram; new stuff settings</screeninfo>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="newstuff-settings.png" format="PNG"/>
</imageobject>
<textobject>
<phrase>&kanagram; newstuff settings</phrase>
</textobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para>
Click the <guibutton>Download new vocabulary</guibutton> button to browse the available online content:
</para>

<screenshot>
<screeninfo>&kanagram; new stuff dialog</screeninfo>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="newstuff-dialog.png" format="PNG"/>
</imageobject>
<textobject>
<phrase>&kanagram; new stuff dialog</phrase>
</textobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para>
To install a vocabulary from the Internet, click on the vocabulary item in the list, then press the <guibutton>Install</guibutton> button to install to your system. The downloaded vocabulary will then be available to play immediately.
</para>

</sect1>
